WEBVTT

00:02.045 --> 00:07.106
the worst criminal offenders are pursued
by the detectives of the Major Case Squad.

00:07.106 --> 00:10.026
These are their stories.

00:12.822 --> 00:14.583
Not this again.

00:14.583 --> 00:15.773
What do you think you're gonna find?

00:15.773 --> 00:18.539
Motel receipts? Love letters?

00:18.539 --> 00:21.539
Lyz, why are you doing this?

00:24.272 --> 00:27.272
Why are you, Henry?

00:28.008 --> 00:31.008
I think she's having me followed.

00:32.274 --> 00:33.995
I don't know what's wrong with her.

00:33.995 --> 00:35.836
Yesterday she left me nine messages,

00:35.836 --> 00:38.836
telling me to be careful.

00:39.654 --> 00:41.149
I gave the cook the night off.

00:41.149 --> 00:43.990
I thought we could all
have dinner at Mr. Chow's.

00:43.990 --> 00:45.753
Uh, sorry, Mom.
I have to work.

00:45.753 --> 00:48.033
I can't make it either.
I have to fly to Miami.

00:48.033 --> 00:50.384
I won't be back till after midnight.

00:50.384 --> 00:52.762
I can do an early lunch,
around 11:00.

00:52.762 --> 00:54.156
I can swing that.

00:54.156 --> 00:55.286
I'm busy.

00:55.286 --> 00:57.125
Never mind.

00:57.125 --> 01:00.125
I just wanted us all to have dinner.

01:04.986 --> 01:05.925
If I were less trusting,

01:05.925 --> 01:08.925
I'd think she's the one having the affair.

01:14.309 --> 01:17.437
I told you I'm gonna prove
how wrong you are, and I will.

01:17.437 --> 01:18.791
Stay out of it, Clayton.

01:18.791 --> 01:20.262
Please?

01:21.313 --> 01:24.313
You and Dad are
not splitting up over this bull.

01:28.941 --> 01:30.906
Big hands, great ass, ponytail...

01:30.906 --> 01:32.176
Oh, what was his name?

01:32.176 --> 01:34.444
Lyz, you remember that
Welsh masseur at Bliss?

01:34.444 --> 01:35.368
No.

01:36.334 --> 01:37.540
It's gonna be a boy.

01:37.540 --> 01:38.769
What?

01:38.769 --> 01:41.697
Oh, you mean Livvy...
my sister-in-law.

01:41.697 --> 01:44.171
We just found out
Monday she's pregnant again.

01:44.171 --> 01:47.256
But how did you know?

01:47.256 --> 01:49.444
Did she go off her Xanax?

01:49.444 --> 01:50.738
Clayton, it's Mom again.

01:50.738 --> 01:52.288
Would you please, please,
give me a call.

01:52.288 --> 01:54.414
I just want to make sure you're okay.

01:54.414 --> 01:57.414
I'll try you at work again.

