No, he still hasn't called.

02:14.133 --> 02:16.282
I just have this terrible...

02:18.431 --> 02:23.137
Yes, it would help.
Are you sure?

02:23.137 --> 02:25.488
Thank you.

02:25.488 --> 02:28.255
Yes, I'm... I'm sitting down.

02:28.255 --> 02:32.586
Oh, man, I can't believe
how much that girl drank.

02:32.586 --> 02:35.586
It looks like she helped
this guy park his car.

02:37.052 --> 02:40.184
Hey, wait.
What's that? A little TV?

02:40.184 --> 02:41.435
It's a video monitor.

02:41.435 --> 02:43.014
Somebody left it on.

02:43.014 --> 02:45.467
It's a live transmission from a camera.

02:45.467 --> 02:48.020
It's got to be close.

02:48.020 --> 02:51.585
Trunk's open.

